text: (dutare), heliri; nanantu nim'mante obba manava matranagiddene. Pujegar'hanada nim'ma devanu obbanu matranendu nanage divyasandesavannu nidalagide. Innu, tanna odeyanannu bhetiyagalikkide emba nirikse ullavanu, olleya kelasavanne madali mattu tanna odeyana pujeyalli bere yarannu palugolisadirali
